description._content: L to R 2nd row: Isobel Fraser, Jean McIntyre, Bell Coleman, Alice Petts, Eileen Massey, Marie Knoble, Em Frauenfelder. Front row: Arthur Petts, Ollie Frauenfelder, Colin Fraser, Kingsley King. L to R back row: Charlie Lankester, Bun English, Bert Winnel, Ken Coleman, Adeline English, Masie McIntyre, Lizzie Massey, Madge English. 3rd row: Frank Massey, Ted Clee, Andy McIntyre, Leo English, George Lankester, Clarrie Joseph, Eric Nye, Fred Nye - Thurgoona Public School, NSW Format: Photograph Find more detailed information about this photograph: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/item/itemDetailPaged.aspx?itemID=388827 Search for more great images in the State Library's collections: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/search/SimpleSearch.aspx From the collection of the State Library of New South Wales www.sl.nsw.gov.au
